==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sostenuto
<hw>Sos`te*nu"to</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[It.]</ety>
<fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>Sustained; -- applied to a movement or passage
the sounds of which are to sustained to the utmost of the nominal value
of the time; also, to a passage the tones of which are to be somewhat
prolonged or protacted.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

